I am writing to express my disappointment and frustration with the service I received at the Ola
 Experience Centre in Vashi. On [22/1/2025], I visited the centre with my family, seeking to charge my Ola scooter. Unfortunately, the experience was subpar.

I explained that my scooter's charge was depleting rapidly, making it impossible for me to travel to the other centre. Shariq's behavior was unprofessional and rude. As a customer, I expect a certain level of service, especially from a brand like Ola.

I hope you take necessary actions to address this issue and ensure better customer experiences in the future. Until then, I will be sharing my disappointing experience with friends and family, advising them to reconsider purchasing Ola scooter.
